{"tid":1960560,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"MCU檔期大執位　《黑寡婦》敲定11月上映","createTime":"2020-04-06T08:35:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T08:54:03.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"631e0d5543b93171f6a6b0d6450f8a88ce68b279","tid":1960560,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:35:45.000Z","msg":"因疫情持續，早前不少電影公司都宣佈將電影延期，包括漫威及DC的多部英雄片，迪士尼亦宣佈將英雄電影檔期大執位，重新定出MCU（漫威電影宇宙）第四階段的正式上映日期，原定本月底上映的《黑寡婦》將延至11月6日上映，安祖蓮娜祖莉（Angelina Jolie）主演的《永恆族》就順延至明年2月12日《上氣》的檔期，而《上氣》則調到明年5月7日上映。《上氣》上月在澳洲開拍，但因疫情關係要停機，主演的梁朝偉、林路迪都身在澳洲。<br />\n<br />\n《奇異博士2》改期至明年11月5日、《雷神奇俠4》則於2022年2月18日上映、《Marvel隊長2》安排於2022年7月8日上映，而已舉行首映禮，但臨時腰斬劉亦菲主演的《花木蘭》將於今年7月24日上映。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1240657/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82-MCU%E6%AA%94%E6%9C%9F%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%B7%E4%BD%8D-%E9%BB%91%E5%AF%A1%E5%A9%A6-%E6%95%B2%E5%AE%9A11%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%8A%E6%98%A0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1240657%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582-MCU%25E6%25AA%2594%25E6%259C%259F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259F%25B7%25E4%25BD%258D-%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%25AF%25A1%25E5%25A9%25A6-%25E6%2595%25B2%25E5%25AE%259A11%25E6%259C%2588%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%2598%25A0&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLS8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=4ff5aa9e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1240657%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582-MCU%25E6%25AA%2594%25E6%259C%259F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259F%25B7%25E4%25BD%258D-%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%25AF%25A1%25E5%25A9%25A6-%25E6%2595%25B2%25E5%25AE%259A11%25E6%259C%2588%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%2598%25A0&h=619c6abf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1240657/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82-MCU%E6%AA%94%E6%9C%9F%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%B7%E4%BD%8D-%E9%BB%91%E5%AF%A1%E5%A9%A6-%E6%9